From 50057622aef42e8adffe903e01b1a15bf1070357 Mon Sep 17 00:00:00 2001
From: =?UTF-8?q?Ren=C3=AA=20de=20Souza=20Pinto?= <rene@renesp.com.br>
Date: Tue, 23 Jun 2026 17:47:31 +0200
Subject: [PATCH 17/21] usb: dwc3: Return in case of fail for probing
MIME-Version: 1.0
Content-Type: text/plain; charset=UTF-8
Content-Transfer-Encoding: 8bit

Return from xhci_dwc3_probe() when it fails to initialize. Without the
fix from this commit, Raspberry Pi 5 crashes at boot:

  DRAM:  8 GiB
  RPI 5 Model B (0xd04170)
  Core:  31 devices, 13 uclasses, devicetree: board
  MMC:   mmc@fff000: 0, mmc@1100000: 1
  Loading Environment from FAT... Error: unknown compression type.
  Unable to read "uboot.env" from mmc0:1...
  In:    serial,usbkbd
  Out:   serial,vidconsole
  Err:   serial,vidconsole
  Net:   No ethernet found.

  PCIe BRCM: link up, 5.0 Gbps x4 (!SSC)
  starting USB...
  this is not a DesignWare USB3 DRD Core
  "Synchronous Abort" handler, esr 0x96000021, far 0x1f00200103
  elr: 000000000004979c lr : 000000000004a920 (reloc)
  elr: 000000003fb7379c lr : 000000003fb74920
  x0 : 0000001f002000ff x1 : 0000001f00200000
  x2 : 0000001f002000ff x3 : 0000000000000005
  x4 : 0000000000000000 x5 : 000000003f71c084
  x6 : 0000000000009d64 x7 : 0000000000009d59
  x8 : 0000000000000003 x9 : 000000003f7122f0
  x10: 000000003f711d7c x11: 0000000000009d50
  x12: 0000000000003fdc x13: 000000003f711ddc
  x14: 000000003f7122f0 x15: 000000003f711f10
  x16: 000000003fb4a798 x17: 0000000000000000
  x18: 000000003f725d90 x19: 0000001f002000ff
  x20: 000000003f7274e0 x21: 0000001f002000ff
  x22: 0000001f00200000 x23: 000000003fbda597
  x24: 000000003fbead20 x25: 0000000000000000
  x26: 0000000000000000 x27: 0000000000000000
  x28: 000000003f7313d0 x29: 000000003f711ec0

Signed-off-by: Renê de Souza Pinto <rene@renesp.com.br>
---
 drivers/usb/host/xhci-dwc3.c | 4 +++-
 1 file changed, 3 insertions(+), 1 deletion(-)

diff --git a/drivers/usb/host/xhci-dwc3.c b/drivers/usb/host/xhci-dwc3.c
index 8ad07a4b98c..a7c4b8ec0a2 100644
--- a/drivers/usb/host/xhci-dwc3.c
+++ b/drivers/usb/host/xhci-dwc3.c
@@ -184,7 +184,9 @@ static int xhci_dwc3_probe(struct udevice *dev)
 
 	dwc3_reg = (struct dwc3 *)((char *)(hccr) + DWC3_REG_OFFSET);
 
-	dwc3_core_init(dwc3_reg);
+	ret = dwc3_core_init(dwc3_reg);
+	if (ret)
+		return ret;
 
 	/* Set dwc3 usb2 phy config */
 	reg = readl(&dwc3_reg->g_usb2phycfg[0]);
-- 
2.53.0

